{"tid":1334025,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[721見］［推上置頂］散水時注意事項","createTime":"2019-07-20T03:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:14:07.000Z","uid":150907,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29d1358762411703f2c3573cfce7b8bf3801f627","tid":1334025,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"上post<br />\n<br />\n從直播中嘅警方的呼籲學到一樣新嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n尋晚討論之後<br />\n<br />\n反覆思量，再定此下策。<br />\n<br />\n綜合幾次衝突，克警在大規模清場前會有以下幾步：<br />\n<br />\n一. 上裝備<br />\n<br />\n二. 開始包圍<br />\n<br />\n三. 開始開咪呼籲示威者和平散去 <br />\n（通常最少都嗌十幾分鐘俾CCTXB影低畫面，之後好等一哥之後讀稿：警方有俾足夠時間呼籲示威者和平散去）<br />\n<br />\n四. 發出最後警告<br />\n （通常都嗌幾分鐘俾CCTXB影底，俾一哥可以讀稿：警方已作出最後警告，只係示威者唔理會，所以迫不得已要清場。）<br />\n<br />\n我哋要扭轉形勢，要一哥同政府無稿可以讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此策在警方進行第三步時用<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲後，我哋作出示威者呼籲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「好啊，阿Sir，我哋唔想犯法，俾條路我哋返屋企。」<br />\n<br />\n「阿Sir唔好包圍，搞到我哋非法佔路，我哋愛香港唔想犯法。」<br />\n<br />\n「阿Sir，你封住哂啲路，咁多人點走啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「阿Sir開路，好迫啊，你哋迫到我哋非法集結勒。」<br />\n<br />\n可能差佬當堂hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚有人討論過：714做過啦，差佬唔聽，無畫面出街㗎<br />\n<br />\n要記住，呢啲呼籲係要由示威者人堆度講出嚟，最好集眾人之口，唔好淨得一兩個。<br />\n<br />\n俾個畫面聲音人睇，成大堆示威者係想和平散去，係警察唔俾人走。<br />\n<br />\n之前點解唔得？因為由議員或其他人一兩個咁出嚟講，會俾人打做成個感覺係果班人包庇我哋，阻礙警方執法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋要連呢個觀念都扭轉埋，示威者要係準確時刻發聲，我哋係想遵從警方呼籲和平散去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋直播世界係無遠弗屆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />示威者呼籲有多國語言版更好。不過留意，講嘅時候唔好疊聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最好五至十個人講完一句，之後回氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，搵另外五至十個人再講另一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講稿創作現正開放俾各位有創意嘅巴絲，最好短而精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你知啦，前線瞬息萬變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，傘陣係需要，只不過係俾大家知，我哋只係保護後撤，唔係再前進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，睇完煙花走出海傍位置啊都要個幾鐘啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多人都要有合理時間散㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n救國上策仲未諗到，唯有出下策救人為上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅決響應警方呼籲，和平散去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n721見，因時制宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03c5d4f0efbda50566f19fdd800f4a870f772e2","tid":1334025,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863b39b017ced16079480cbb6f8934df239c2b59","tid":1334025,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"721 新香港<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3usgiZp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3usgiZp.png&h=14aab743&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"849df3d728fbabf2f2c8d66ee36601e9e151ffbe","tid":1334025,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3040f02c4152bc11865511df2e668262a083c57f","tid":1334025,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s